profile:
Royal Oak Design And Build is a family owned landscape construction and design firm located out of Tavistock, Ontario. We offer services ranging from Patios, seating walls, water features/ponds, decks, pergolas, retaining walls, gardens, edging, mulching, planting, and more! 

We pride ourselves on having fair prices, reliable and honest relationships with our clients, and the highest level of quality and attention to detail that allows your outdoor space to stay beautiful for years to come.

Proudly serving Tavistock, Kitchener, Waterloo, Stratford, Geulph, Woodstock & Surrounding areas
